data.eml:eml: A morphology-based phylogeny of the Liolaemus alticolor – bibronii group (Iguania: Liolaemidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Quinteros, Andrés Sebastián (2013): A morphology-based phylogeny of the Liolaemus alticolor – bibronii group (Iguania: Liolaemidae). Zootaxa 3670 (1): 1-32, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3670.1.1
